    • Constructor Detail

      • Settings

        public Settings(boolean temp,
        boolean windSpeed,
        boolean sky,
        boolean airPressure,
        boolean humidity,
        boolean sunset,
        boolean metric,
        City city,
        boolean precip)
        Creates a settings object. Initialized upon users first use setting boolean values to true if user wishes to view corresponding data.
        Parameters:
        temp - true if user wishes to view temperature
        windSpeed - true if user wishes to view wind speed and direction
        sky - true if user wishes to view sky condition
        airPressure - true if user wishes to view air pressure
        humidity - true if user wishes to view humidity
        sunset - true if user wishes to view sunset and sunrise times
        metric - true if user wishes to view measurements in metric, false if imperial
        city - int value of city ID for current city. Initially chosen upon startup
        precip - true if user wishes to view precipitation for next 24 hours
